{
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Unify is used after setup when you have multiple AI tool configs:\n1. Merge ~/CLAUDE.md, ~/.gemini/GEMINI.md, ~/.codex/AGENTS.md, ~/.config/opencode/AGENTS.md into ~/AGENTS.md\n2. Replace originals with symlinks pointing to ~/AGENTS.md\n3. Identical files are replaced directly without merging\n"
,
"cn"
:
"当你有多个 AI 工具配置文件时使用 unify：\n1. 将 ~/CLAUDE.md、~/.gemini/GEMINI.md、~/.codex/AGENTS.md、~/.config/opencode/AGENTS.md 合并到 ~/AGENTS.md\n2. 原文件替换为指向 ~/AGENTS.md 的 symlink\n3. 内容相同的文件直接替换，无需合并\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent unify"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 合并配置，统一管理"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Merge configs for unified management"
}
]
}

